OL,5, The family of Chris Kaba, an unarmed   
OL,6, black man killed by the Metropolitan   
OL,7, Police in south London, has been shown 
OL,8, body-worn police camera footage of the 
OL,9, moments leading up to his death.       
OL,11,FMr Kaba, 24, was shot dead by an armed 
OL,12,Fofficer following a car pursuit that   
OL,13,Fended in Streatham on 5 September.     
OL,15,FMr Kaba's mother Helen Nkama told the  
OL,16,FBBC it had been "very hard" to watch   
OL,17,Fthe footage.                           
OL,19,FThe family also met the Met Police's   
OL,20,FCommissioner after viewing the footage.
